graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:OAuthCreateClientInput!)
{
	oAuthCreateClient (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		rowId
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		scopeOptions
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
	}
}

	{
		id
		rowId
		grantType
		name
		secret
		authUrl
		redirect
		scopeOptions
		expiredAccessToken
		expiredRefreshToken
		isActive
		isMaster
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
